(45846, 93068, 0, 4, 'Birth of Ground', '', '2012-03-27 00:00:00', 2000, 1, 0, 7, '', 'Rivers of molten lava flow from a mountain womb\nUnder crust of freshly formed earth\nRe-emerging at the water’s edge \nIn a volcanic cone made by\nOcean’s sudden freezing of the seething stream of fire.\n\nOpposing elements converge in primordial creation of the ground\nOn which we stand – glowing liquid stone spewing high into the\nBlack space of night sky – white hot waves crash upon the shore\nGiving birth to the mass of rock growing right before our eyes.\n\nBillowing clouds of steam rising into the air as instant thunderheads\nVibrant orange veins paint light on the dark slopes of the night\nWhite smoke steams from fissures in the silver charcoal\nSkin of new born ground.\n\nIn fearless utter awe we gape at the spectacle of \nThe forces at play\nEarth spews its bile that congeals upon the\nShore in ageless transformation of\nWhat it was before.\n', 449, '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, 0, 0, '2012-03-27 13:37:46', '2015-03-12 13:51:29', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
